Package au.com.permeance.liferay.clojure

This package contains the java runtime for the clojure implementation of a liferay scripting engine.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CallUnderClassLoader<V> This class provides a wrapper for the Callable interface which allows the call to be executed under a different ClassLoader.
ClojureScriptingCallable This class wraps the clojure generated ClojureScriptable protocol and ClojureScriptableImpl implementation classes for execution of scripts from within Liferay.
ClojureScriptingExecutor This class provides the interface between liferay's Scripting API and the clojure scripting runtime.
RegisterClojureExecutorAction This class provides a liferay action which registers the ClojureScriptingExecutor to liferay for script execution.
 

Package au.com.permeance.liferay.clojure Description

This package contains the java runtime for the clojure implementation of a liferay scripting engine.
